        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>If you had 1 million euros, what would you do with it?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 80 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>If i had 1 million euros, i would firstable give a part to my parents because they have been giving me a lot of money since i was born. Then i would buy a normal house and maybe a car if i still have enough money. For the house, a old house in the countryside could be great and for the car, a Clio or a small VW would be really good. One million euros is not so much in fact but it can help a lot !</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B2</span>
                    <note type="comment">b2 tenses and structures. Longer text required to judge vocab and syntax properly.</note>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label subtype="majority-vote" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
